    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2354200/extras/c79e81f1317ac4c3eab0b3a29b47f72a.poster.avif?t=1771680354\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2354200/extras/c79e81f1317ac4c3eab0b3a29b47f72a.webm?t=1771680354\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2354200/extras/c79e81f1317ac4c3eab0b3a29b47f72a.mp4?t=1771680354\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>A polished quick session Action Roguelite designed for immediate fun and replays</strong>. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Advance through stages, fight bosses, beat the game, repeat. Streamlined, quick to start, no interruptions.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Here's some more you'll like about it: </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Dual-purpose design</strong> for every action. Big fan of Downwell here. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Five stages, oddball enemies and bosses. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Dope soundtrack</strong> from WangleLine, tenby. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>LOTS of upgrades</strong>. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Contains a <strong><i><u>Capybara</u></i></strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2354200/extras/b3df4947b6116751045bc101dc758d2f.poster.avif?t=1771680354\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2354200/extras/b3df4947b6116751045bc101dc758d2f.webm?t=1771680354\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><sourc